## 6. API Endpoints Summary

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register` | Public | Register new user |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Public | Login, returns JWT |
| `GET` | `/api/jobs` | Public | List jobs (search, pagination) |
| `GET` | `/api/jobs/:id` | Public | Get single job |
| `POST` | `/api/jobs` | Recruiter | Create new job |
| `POST` | `/api/applications` | Candidate | Apply to job |
| `PATCH` | `/api/applications/:id` | Recruiter | Update application status |
| `PATCH` | `/api/applications/:id/withdraw` | Candidate | Withdraw application |
| `GET` | `/api/applications/job/:jobId` | Recruiter | Get applications for a job |
| `GET` | `/api/applications/my` | Candidate | Get my applications |
| `GET` | `/api/dashboard/stats` | Recruiter/Admin | Dashboard statistics |
| `GET` | `/api/match/job/:jobId` | Recruiter | Get matching candidates |

